    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean Stack is a little puzzle game that involves stacking odd-sized objects with fun physics without making anything touch the ground. Stack thought a huge variety of places and situations. You'll also need to use potions on the objects to get through the levels, which makes the game even more challenging! <br><br><strong>About Clean Stack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Clean Stack is a extended version of a game made in the GMTK 2024 gamejam. The game is way longer with a bunch of new mechanics. The game has been designed to provide a pleasant, relaxing experience while retaining some challenge. In addition, there is <u>more bananas</u>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >its literally <strong><u>FREE</u></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>65</i> levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few hours of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ton of fun and <i>weird</i> achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ differents items to play with</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few potions with each unique effects on items to make chaotic situations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An awesome <u>green</u> monster to <span class=\"bb_strike\">annoy</span> guide you though the game !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different gameplay alterations, such as a hard mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bananas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And all the passion of a team in their creation</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bananas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And maybe more <span class=\"bb_strike\">bananas</span> content who knows?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276530/extras/febdfebf3ab0a497862b83ddf2b30e3f.avif?t=1771082061\" alt=\"Made by : Babeko, Paçoco, Quazquaz, AllNineAliens\" width=1429 height=1138 /></span></p>",
